Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)}被舍弃的 面具
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像在做噩梦 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗 昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…我说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜…娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥什么也没说 什么也没
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉所期望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉所选择的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而在那里 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是阻碍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉的人身安全有保障
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有布里塔尼亚正规军 还有朱雀在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然作为敌人他们无比棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但棘手也正体现了这保障的可信度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 就像我曾经期望过的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使没有我保护 也已…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你看 听说这个寺庙是一千年前建的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别提这个了 你看到水枪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明准备了大家的份的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,网子 蜡烛 假发 烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有铃鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…我们是去修学旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上 我是第二次了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是太期待修学旅行 兴奋得没睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…其实就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁鲁真像个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11区新总督即将发表就任致辞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请全体同学到礼堂集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是布里塔尼亚第87皇位继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉·V·布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代替日前殉职的卡拉雷斯公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出任本届11区总督
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我双目失明且腿脚不便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总督？那样的小女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还请各位多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说多多关照…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄得我都乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然匆忙 有一事希望大家能协助于我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算重建日本行政特区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟说出这种犯忌的话来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在日本特区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚人和属区人民将受到平等对待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11区人可以重获日本人之名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她刚才说日本人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又想欺骗我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木朱雀也在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他也一样是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是杀戮公主的骑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出卖ZERO的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然过去在日本特区曾发生过不幸的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我认为其目标并没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平等 温柔的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也请务必加入日本特区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还来？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今还…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承认彼此的错误 一定可以重来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我坚信这点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓我一跳 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会说出重建日本特区…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 尤菲皇姐想做的事是正确的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 错的不是尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换乘急行列车的乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请在下车后到站台对面的3号线等待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一站可换乘千京线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,470)\fad(0,700)}各站停车将在5号站台…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,470)}已经不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是ZERO 还是我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个总督也和杀戮公主尤菲米娅一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 日本人谁也不会参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用甜言蜜语把人引出来 然后赶尽杀绝？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:06:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少瞧不起人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 今后怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是跟布里塔尼亚决战了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的Knightmare可只剩下红莲一架了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 只要ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐耶殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉城先生说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但怎么不见ZERO大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新婚妻子特地赶来的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在中华联邦时他也连封信都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是出轨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人 他是骗人的 神乐耶殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓英雄爱美人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉴于成年男子的生理状况…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮大忙了 你比看起来更成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在的时候 感谢你陪伴他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不足挂齿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 卡莲小姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支持ZERO大人的三位…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是三宫女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}注：三宫女是女儿节用来装饰的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫女？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说要追寻黑色骑士团 出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精密检查还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点还是老样子 他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了完成Conquista…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑麦面包加黄姜 日本砂糖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混合后再加芥末酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今为止所作所为 都是为了娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是布里塔尼亚第87皇位继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉·V·布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:09:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代替日前殉职的卡拉雷斯公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么 小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉或许已察觉了我的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但即使如此 她还是说要继承尤菲的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是为了这 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了先给钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了 穷光蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,败家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 你们不也一样是11区人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要这个 就拿钱来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本人吃日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是以布里塔尼亚人走狗的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说日本人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要布里塔尼亚人同情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区学生少管人家做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是自愿为我所用的 学生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰我 贱民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我做俯卧撑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科尔恰克先生 您做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下蹲运动 嗥叫 拍手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 1 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不回这儿来也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 他活着更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能…光是不当ZERO那很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:10:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也不是多浪漫的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这样下去 黑色骑士团就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「为娜娜莉而存在的ZERO」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修这么说呢 玛莉安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道 他到底想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然来了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是ZERO…你开始的地方
Comment: 0,0:00:00.94,0:00:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以靠这个回到怀念的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别胡闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是失败了一次又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再想作战计划挽回不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像往常一样下命令给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开Knightmare？还是诱饵搜查？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么我都听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安慰我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用女人才能做到的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给了我们梦想 就要负责任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把我们骗到底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定要把完美的ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演到底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任务是监视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些都是痛苦的重负
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是 黑色骑士团是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 娜娜莉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是为了娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO消失的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11区就能获得和平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥也恢复到普通学生的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福生活就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追求幸福 有什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会伤害到任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还可以将一切归零
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 只有我不会去任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远和哥哥在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何志愿提出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出任ZERO复活后的11区总督
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前一直受到哥哥的保护
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在虽然他行踪不明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他一定还在关注着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要做出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会给哥哥丢脸的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很重哦 那面具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还需要肩负整个世界的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是必须有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是布里塔尼亚军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵舰所属及航路 与申报有异
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请停船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在将进行强行临检
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:14:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将等待十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前所有乘员解除武装
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到甲板上站好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 大家都去修学旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要追上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 空无一人的鸟笼正适合现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来了 鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修也来放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭用剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？修学旅行呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是就我们去了 你会哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键不在于去哪里 而是跟谁一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说能实现愿望 就做了试试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过怎么也想不起是跟谁学的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你许了什么愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经实现了 一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和大家一起放烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼娜 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有鲁路修和罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只折了一只 所以只实现了鲁鲁这份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得以前曾跟娜娜莉 朱雀说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若幸福有形态的话 那会是怎样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是了 就像朱雀说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许幸福就像玻璃一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为平时从未察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它确实存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证据就是 稍微改变看的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玻璃就会映照出光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:17:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比任何东西更雄辩地主张自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说折一千只这种纸鹤 就能实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉想许什么愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望有一个温柔的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔的世界就近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使为虚伪的记忆所玷污
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却更显出透明的琉璃色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.63,0:17:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 永远
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁鲁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哭什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我们的友情所感动了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也有可爱的一面嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再来这里一起放烟花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定 一定要再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不仅是为了娜娜莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 爆破油轮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使敌方声纳失效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下俯配平30度 急速潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的联络呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依然断绝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该又打算潜入海底逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出动PortmanII
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以被动模式确认
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从动力音判断应该是水中型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降低深度 被发现就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ASROC（反潜导弹）发射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要惊慌 这是无的放矢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以θ地点为中心张开包围网
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能把敌人逼出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰内各部进水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一移动会被对方捕捉到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Q1 听到吗 Q1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下俯配平50度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向地点L14急速潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 太迟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续投放深水炸弹 保持包围网
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝向正面 鱼雷全弹发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用定时信管设40秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了相信他 还有别的办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设定信管后 全弹发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认鱼雷发射音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉到敌方位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人在地点L14
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中攻击 等它浮上我来捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnsimsun\fs16\pos(320,442)\b}火蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnsimsun\fs16\pos(565,442)}蓝海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Salamander呼叫BlueDolphin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向定点改变发射角度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Portman布阵区域 传送
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,网眼不大 别设错目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是Salamander 已确认
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标设定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸弹投射管 旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,固定锚后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各员 准备承受冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 甲烷水合物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浮力…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:20:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木卿 水泡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水泡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转舵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 即将翻船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海底涌起巨大的水泡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 这不是叫援军就能解决的问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合幸存的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将黑色骑士团…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO往这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.86,0:21:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的回答吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪就是违抗君令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定接受娜娜莉总督的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就是日本特区的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是投降了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.95,0:21:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO下令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:21:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团全员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入日本特区！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你确实正面带笑容 正在享受
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.72,0:23:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 那并非真实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.41,0:23:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐藏在你那笑容背后的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.00,0:23:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若只有一人知道真相 拥有救赎的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 那么我理当反抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:23:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是名为和平的统治
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.78,0:24:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蔑视 欺瞒我们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我们视作玩物的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.23,0:24:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以ZERO的名义…
